==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Scaphognathite
<hw>Sca*phog"na*thite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>ska`fh</grk> boat + <grk>gna`qos</grk> jaw.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A thin leaflike appendage (the exopodite) of the
second maxilla of decapod crustaceans. It serves as a pumping organ to
draw the water through the gill cavity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scaphoid</ent>⟦br⟧
